	<text xml:id="import-1665323279611">
		<body>
			<pb facs="https://fromthepage.com/image-service/705620/full/full/0/native.jpg" n="1" xml:id="F705620"/>
			<div xml:id="OTP705620">
				<fw type="pageNum">1</fw>
				<opener/>
				<dateline><abbr>Cpl.</abbr> Ann Smith<lb/>Co. 6 22nd Regt.<lb/> Fort Oglethorpe Ga</dateline>
				<dateline>[POSTMARK]<lb/> FORT OGLETHORPE GA 1943<lb/> APR 17 5- PM</dateline>
				<dateline/>
				<p xml:id="OTP705620P2">
					<listPerson>
						<person>
							<persName>Mrs. G. W. Carlstead<lb/> 1102 Dillon Drive<lb/> St. Louis. Mo.</persName>
						</person>
					</listPerson>
				</p>
			</div>
			<pb facs="https://fromthepage.com/image-service/705621/full/full/0/native.jpg" n="2" xml:id="F705621"/>
			<div xml:id="OTP705621">
				<fw type="pageNum">2</fw>
				<p xml:id="OTP705621P0">Fort Oglethorpe Ga<lb/> Friday night</p>
				<p xml:id="OTP705621P1">Dear Kids</p>
				<p xml:id="OTP705621P2">
					<listPerson>
						<person>
							<persName>Arrived back in camp OK. Everyone<lb/> seemed glad to see me back. Got a new<lb/> Co. in the next day. I am acting Supply <lb/> Sgt now. Hope I make good as I can <lb/> get my rating soon. Gave out over 600<lb/> pieces of clothing + kept the records straight. <lb/> Director Hobbes was here today and they had<lb/> a big parade for him.</persName>
						</person>
					</listPerson>
				</p>
				<p xml:id="OTP705621P3">A new order came out + we can't wear<lb/> any more civilian clothes. A lot of trouble<lb/> for nothing. So I just sent mine back. <lb/> I'll send you kids something for your <lb/> anniversary the first of the month<lb/> after I get paid. What wouldyou <lb/> like to have?</p>
				<p xml:id="OTP705621P4">How are the boys? Did Jimmy have <lb/> whooping cough? I sure miss</p>
			</div>
			<pb facs="https://fromthepage.com/image-service/705622/full/full/0/native.jpg" n="3" xml:id="F705622"/>
			<div xml:id="OTP705622">
				<fw type="pageNum">3</fw>
				<p xml:id="OTP705622P0">them after I have been home + then leave.</p>
				<p xml:id="OTP705622P1">What did Lucille say about her<lb/> picture?</p>
				<p xml:id="OTP705622P2">Don't know anything to write so<lb/> will say good night for this time. <lb/> Write soon. Love To All</p>
				<p xml:id="OTP705622P3">Mother</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
